properties.areaDesc: Grand Marais to Whitefish Point MI; Lake Superior from Grand Marais MI to Whitefish Point MI 5NM off shore to the US/Canadian border
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued March 1 at 4:29AM EST until March 2 at 11:00AM EST by NWS Marquette MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and waves
7 to 10 feet expected.

* WHERE...Grand Marais to Whitefish Point MI and Lake Superior
from Grand Marais MI to Whitefish Point MI 5NM off shore to
the US/Canadian border.

* WHEN...From midnight tonight to 11 AM EST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM MIDNIGHT TONIGHT TO 11 AM EST MONDAY
